CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779113475
OL,3,CGuernsey's Merrien takes 5th world
OL,4,Ctitle down under
OL,6,FThe 56-year-old topped her group
OL,7,Fbefore winning her quarter-final and
OL,8,Fsemi-final matches to reach the final.
OL,10,FSpeaking to World Bowls after the
OL,11,Ffinal, Merrien said it felt:
OL,12,F"Absolutely fantastic. It's been a
OL,13,Fcracking week, and just to finish on a
OL,14,Fhigh like this is amazing.
OL,16,F"Each one gets better with age,
OL,17,Fbecause the older you get, the harder
OL,18,Fit is, and I never thought I'd be back
OL,19,Fhere winning a World Championship, so
OL,20,FI'm just enjoying the moment."
