OL,3,CGuernsey's Merrien takes 5th world
OL,4,Ctitle down under
OL,6,FHer victory comes just over a year
OL,7,Fafter she and husband Ian Merrien won
OL,8,Fbronze in the mixed pairs at the 2025
OL,9,FWorld Bowls Indoor Championships.
OL,11,FMerrien has represented Guernsey for
OL,12,Fdecades and remains one of the
OL,13,Fisland's most successful athletes,
OL,14,Fwith major honours across World,
OL,15,FBritish Isles, Commonwealth, and
OL,16,FIsland Games competitions.
