OL,3,CGuernsey's Merrien takes 5th world
OL,4,Ctitle down under
OL,6,FLater this year, she'll represent
OL,7,FGuernsey internationally again after
OL,8,Fshe was selected as one of 20 athletes
OL,9,Fwho'll travel to Glasgow for the
OL,10,FCommonwealth Games.
OL,12,FShe was made an MBE in 2016 for
OL,13,Fservices to bowls.
